#*:''He lied about his past military service and had [spent] recent years being a $200/hr '''manwhore'''.''
# A [[promiscuous]] man who has no regard for his sexual partners or the emotional value of his relationships.
#*'''2005''' July 6, Jennifer Balderas, ''Daddy's Little <strike>Girl</strike> Demon'' [sic.], Finding Her Life, at jennerallyspeaking.com
#*:''Apparently these guys are total horndogs and '''manwhores''' and yadda yadda.''
